snippet.title: Forza Motorsport 6 Announce Video
snippet.description:
Forza Motorsport 6, exclusive to Xbox One, announced an all-new Ford GT cover car revealed at North American International Auto Show

For more information, please visit: http://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/forza-6
